# Design System

- Cursor/Vercel-inspired but original — no brand asset copying.
- Tokenized styling only (`src/theme/tokens.zig`).
- Dark-first, high contrast, hairline borders, compact panels, keyboard-first.
- Agent surface: task cards, composer, status labels — original layout.
